ltris
------------------------------------------
SDL Tetris game

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.5.25-7
  libSDL12-1.2.12-1
  libSDL_mixer-1.2.8-1
  libintl8-0.15-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding devel packages)
  autoconf2.5-2.61-1
  automake1.9-1.9.6-2
  binutils-20060817-1
  cygport-0.3.8-1
  gawk-3.1.6-1
  gcc-core-3.4.4-3
  make-3.81-1
  sed-4.1.5-2

Canonical website:
  http://lgames.sourceforge.net/

Canonical download:
  http://downloads.sourceforge.net/lgames/

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack ltris-1.0.12-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./ltris-1.0.12-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/ltris-1.0.12-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/ltris-1.0.12-X.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

